    "summary": "The user explores the concept of \"fake news,\" asking whether it is a genuine phenomenon or merely a rhetorical tool used for delegitimization. The assistant provides a descriptive analysis of media fragmentation and eventually answers a direct question regarding the difference between bias and lying, while noting the weaponization of the term by politicians.",
